{"tid":1746683,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關投唔投泛民 我想講句公道說話","createTime":"2019-11-23T00:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T05:37:51.000Z","uid":53515,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f3841090b2a542651fd2af6315765969e10ce1f","tid":1746683,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T00:33:26.000Z","msg":"大大聲屌泛民係假本土 真建制<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母咁有理想你又唔落場選？你落場咪投你囉！<br />\n<br />\n本土落場必投本土<br />\n<br />\n但假如果區咁撚多人撐本土 但又冇人出嚟參選 <br />\n<br />\n講乜撚嘢理想？<br />\n<br />\n好簡單，本土&gt;泛民 <br />\n<br />\n總知我要建制輸 就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n打泛民一定易過打建制"},{"pid":"4ba47e4fc25bee517593d1e3907e554bdb784744","tid":1746683,"uid":328199,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T00:34:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">取消偽選舉喇<br />\n垃圾販民<br />\n邊個唔知你哋以前做過咩<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n呃下啲新移民同支那人就叻</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n掌心雷點破解<br />\n賄選點破解<br />\n種票點破解<br />\n中國配票點破解<br />\n<br />\n真係垃撚圾<br />\n<br />\n革命喇仆街<br />\n仲選你呀媽臭閪<br />\n都唔撚係選舉<br />\n唔公平唔公開唔公正<br />\n仲話咩公投喎<br />\n你老味係咪逐張逐張票打開俾你睇投邊個先<br />\n中國配完票就話民意傾向中國<br />\n一次偽選舉否定咗過往香港人嘅努力<br />\n文宣做幾多都變成廢嗡<br />\n人死幾多都淨係送頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人乜你仲信咁嘅選舉唔係呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但最後我會含淚投垃圾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命還革命<br />\n革命仍然會繼續<br />\n如果唔係點對得住死去嘅手足</span></span>"},{"pid":"e23acdf1578097eb8ec587b2685ab91cad5582af","tid":1746683,"uid":155837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"#2乜都紅字睇到好辛苦，仲要睇唔明係想射落海定取消選舉定係投泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw認同樓主<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">總之要建制輸</span></span>"},{"pid":"6ff91f4747d8732aaf3f3b0a471cae8cf2982363","tid":1746683,"uid":127410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/u/7307626295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fu%2F7307626295&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvguu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=a16992d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/u/7307626295</a><br />\n對家做曬野啦"},{"pid":"a865b5285bb2aff37a3c6374eafe2c6ee504012c","tid":1746683,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50a626fe0863d35d72e07f2106709a5a8395f01","tid":1746683,"uid":82912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"講話投白票 廢票 唔投果D一定係鬼<br />\n唔投就等如俾建制羸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8313f25b3317c89e79b8346866766022e23be1bd","tid":1746683,"uid":311867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50a626fe0863d35d72e07f2106709a5a8395f01","tid":1746683,"uid":82912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"講話投白票 廢票 唔投果D一定係鬼<br />\n唔投就等如俾建制羸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n樓上已有一個<br />\n成日話唔好投票搞革命<br />\n但果班人一定唔係前線"},{"pid":"04ce5e4f170dc4a030eeca4e333275c9d1ddb886","tid":1746683,"uid":109115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}